<!-- FAQ -->
<section id="faq" style="padding:100px max(5vw,24px)">
  <div style="max-width:720px;margin:0 auto">
    <div class="section-label">FAQ</div>
    <h2 style="margin-bottom:40px">Common questions</h2>
    <div id="faq-list">
      <div class="faq-item"><div class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">Do customers know they're talking to an AI? <span class="faq-arrow">▾</span></div><div class="faq-a">That's your choice. Most businesses configure Aria to introduce herself as a "virtual receptionist" which is accurate and transparent. You can customise exactly what she says in her greeting.</div></div>
      <div class="faq-item"><div class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">What happens when a call goes over the plan limit? <span class="faq-arrow">▾</span></div><div class="faq-a">Additional calls will politely let callers know your lines are busy and offer voicemail. You'll be notified to upgrade. We never cut off mid-call.</div></div>
      <div class="faq-item"><div class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">Can I keep my existing phone number? <span class="faq-arrow">▾</span></div><div class="faq-a">Yes — you can forward your existing number to your RingDesk number, or port your number over to Twilio. Both options work. We'll guide you through it in the setup process.</div></div>
      <div class="faq-item"><div class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">How long does setup take? <span class="faq-arrow">▾</span></div><div class="faq-a">Most businesses are live within 30 minutes. Create an account, get a phone number, write your AI prompt, and point Twilio at your server. Our step-by-step guide walks you through everything.</div></div>
      <div class="faq-item"><div class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">What languages does Aria speak? <span class="faq-arrow">▾</span></div><div class="faq-a">Aria currently works best in English. Multi-language support (French, Spanish, German, and more) is on our roadmap for later this year.</div></div>
      <div class="faq-item"><div class="faq-q" onclick="toggleFaq(this)">Can I cancel anytime? <span class="faq-arrow">▾</span></div><div class="faq-a">Absolutely. No lock-in, no cancellation fees. Cancel from your billing dashboard and your account stays active until the end of your billing period.</div></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

